metadata.title: Harlequin duck Sites in  PWS

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  This data set depicts the harlequin duck survey locations in eastern and western Prince William Sound. Data was provided by ADF&G and automated by the EVOS Trustee Council GIS division.
